    "question_timestamp": "2025-09-24T19:26:01Z",
    "question_text": "I recently asked a question regarding the prime meridian on earth. In the case of earth, the location of the prime meridian is arbitrary, and many cities have enjoyed that place of geographical privilege throughout history. However, in the case of the moon, the prime meridian is an easy choice. How is the prime meridian for the moon defined?",
